{"tid":666584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[QR關請入] 金管局快速支付系統測試中，擬９月推","createTime":"2018-05-16T03:51:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T06:57:19.000Z","uid":1159,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2ccb2a636812195610d7be21b2e69bbfdad00453","tid":666584,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T03:51:57.000Z","msg":"<strong>金管局快速支付系統測試中，擬９月推</strong><br />\n<br />\n16/05/2018 08:23<br />\n<br />\n金管局鐵定９月推出快速支付系統，金管局總裁陳德霖昨指，該局亦希望見到跨境支付，冀粵港澳大灣區會有相關措施細則出台，在區內作先行先試。　　至於打通本地銀行及儲值支付工具之間的快速支付系統，金管局副總裁李達志表示，快速支付系統已完成開發工作，未來兩個月將開放予銀行接入進行測試。　　他又稱，<strong>當局就統一二維碼（ＱＲ　Ｃｏｄｅ）標準的技術方案經已完成</strong>，<strong>屆時商戶「不會再成枱ＱＲ　Ｃｏｄｅ」，而是一個二維碼即可接通不同電子錢包</strong>。《香港經濟日報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=latest&amp;newsid=ETN280516513\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Fcategorized_news_detail.php%3Fcategory%3Dlatest%26newsid%3DETN280516513&d=duMjyfxHMcZJy4sLcEKbzAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=3f168fb7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=latest&amp;newsid=ETN280516513</a>"},{"pid":"9e2cfb9b5995ad493d8a45da5e4803271d851917","tid":666584,"uid":609,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T03:52:58.000Z","msg":"點解唔係用applepay/google pay....<br />\n<br />\n今時今日仲用qr code 學埋贏國d衰野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2b7947f9f9374fa979d2ee4023c01df6a41dc3a","tid":666584,"uid":1159,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"9e2cfb9b5995ad493d8a45da5e4803271d851917","tid":666584,"uid":609,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T03:52:58.000Z","msg":"點解唔係用applepay/google pay....<br />\n<br />\n今時今日仲用qr code 學埋贏國d衰野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T03:54:59.000Z","msg":"QR Code 係俾啲唔打算裝卡機嘅商戶使用，同NFC兩者定位唔